!
!
!	This is a code package solving a Super-Word-Puzzle.
!
!	Usage:
!		Modified 'input.txt' file, you can also add any other input files if you like.
!        	Start the puzzle by typing './run.py input.txt' or '$DIR/python run.py input.txt'.
!        	Have fun.
!	
!	Notice:
!		I use ghost grid in my code. To explain that see the example below:
!			original grid	  (mapping)	ghost grid
!							  EFDEFDE 		
!			    				  HIGHIGH
!			    ABC		    -->		  BCABCAB
!			    DEF		    -->		  EFDEFED
!			    GHI		    -->		  HIGHIGH
!							  BCABCAB
!							  EFDEFDE	
!
!			   N X M	    -->	        (3N-2) X (3M-2)
!
!  	Hong Wu<xunzhangthu@gmail.com>, 2012/10/21
!
!---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
